@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Courier

title envShare - Secret Sync Flow (Push and Pull)

actor Developer
participant "CLI (esai)" as CLI
participant "Backend API" as API
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

== Push ==
Developer -> CLI : esai push .env
CLI -> CLI : Parse .env and classify keys
CLI -> API : POST /api/v1/sync/push
API -> API : Authorize user and project
API -> API : Encrypt key names and values
API -> DB : Upsert secrets / versions / personal values
DB --> API : Commit transaction
API --> CLI : Push result summary
CLI --> Developer : Show changed keys

== Pull ==
Developer -> CLI : esai pull
CLI -> API : GET /api/v1/sync/pull
API -> API : Authorize user and project
API -> DB : Read project secrets + personal values
DB --> API : Encrypted records
API -> API : Decrypt and merge final values
API --> CLI : Plain key/value payload
CLI -> CLI : Render .env content
CLI --> Developer : Write target file

@enduml
